        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="45" name="Message" rows="6" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
"i saw this pharse(about the soloing for a fair risk/reward in a interwiev with the "team".i see no reason to name them as liars)"

I'm sorry but if you still listen to everything software developers tell you and take them seriously I think thats being a little naive.

example:
"Our game is going to be the best!"

Well damn, if they say its going to be the best, I'll just have to assume that they are telling the truth!

Reasons why this game won't be a problem for EQ:
1) Many/most people who play EQ seem to prefer player vs monster type games.  Note: population of PvP servers.
2) Many people perfer the tradiational fantasy world of Norrath to futuristic space world.  ie: swords vs guns.

Assuming that the new games will be wonderful, run flawlessly and be much more fun than EQ is very naive at this point.  Personally I will wait till these other games are done and on the store shelf before I judge what the best game is.



Pharos Plagebringer
55 necro Xev
