ment that and we just won't do that because there are so many of them".  When I read that I almost cried... it's just so pathetic.</P><P>These are reasons why I want to move the hell away from EQ, and reasons why I hope that the new MMORPGs coming out kick EQ's ass.  Verant needs a hell of a wakeup call that they aren't the best in the biz and that yes, customers DO matter.</P><P><table><td><font size=1>Zerfall Et'Krankheit<BR>Gnomish Purveyor of Death and Pestilence</P><P>I have not the need of agents and underlings,<BR>for I am Death...</font id=size1></td></table></font></td>
